                    <l>The Luxury<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to apprehend </l>
                    <l>The Luxury<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 'twould be </l>
                    <l>To look at thee<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a single time </l>
                    <l>An Epicure of<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 me </l>
                    <l>In whatsoever<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Presence makes</l>
                    <l>Till for a further<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Food<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>I scarcely<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 recollect to starve </l>
                    <l>So first am<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 I supplied.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The Luxury to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 meditate </l>
                    <l>The Luxury<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 it was</l>
                    <l>To banquet on<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thy Countenance </l>
                    <l>A Sumptuousness<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 supplies<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>To plainer Days<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 whose table far </l>
                    <l>As Certainty can<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 see </l>
                    <l>Is laden with<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a single Crumb</l>
                    <l>The Consciousness<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of thee </l>
